    name: "Alex Fries",
    title: "National Council member, former chapter president Nu Beta",
    blurb: "Joining Phi Mu Delta is about more than joining a chapter. It is about joining a brotherhood of future friends, colleagues and partners in your pursuit of the common good, no matter the arena you choose to enter. Conclave is where that ideal becomes real.",
